'''''Biggs Darklighter: Blaze of Glory''''' was a short comic scheduled to appear in an issue of ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]'', detailing how [[Biggs Darklighter/Legends|Biggs Darklighter]] left [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] for the [[Imperial Academy/Legends|Imperial Academy]], his adventures on the [[Rand Ecliptic/Legends|''Rand Ecliptic'']], and his joining the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebellion]]. Its story was presumably the basis for the [[Star Wars: Empire: Darklighter|''Darklighter'']] story arc of ''[[Star Wars: Empire]]''.

